item.description:
The Mighty Demons take on the Nashville Kangaroos this Saturday a few minutes north of Boston in Reading MA.
This ground has a fantastic MCG like surface and with playgrounds for the kids, the barbie fired up and refreshments available this will be a great day out for the family as the game will be a tad earlier and out of the heat of the day.

This will be a couple of hours of hard hitting, fast paced, high scoring football without the pads. Come check it out and cheer us on!

Go Demons!
